      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in exceptional mechanical and cosmetic order. This example features the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been meticulously addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, rod bearing replacement with treated shells, and a multi-plate rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec Bilstein dampers and fresh bushings to maintain original turn-in characteristics. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin shows zero bolster wear or headliner sag. A purist\u2019s specification with a verified service history.",
