      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its class. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a 'time capsule' presentation. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing. All interior plastics and carbon fiber trim pieces are free of scratches, and the vehicle retains its original 'new car' scent, having never been smoked in. Mechanically, this car is in peak condition. It comes with a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists, with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been cared for with an open checkbook policy.",
